                      max_lt_iff.mpr ‚ü®hdpq.trans_lt _, hdq.trans_lt _‚ü©).trans
              (max_eq_left_of_lt _).symm <;> rw [hdp] <;>
                exact WithBot.coe_lt_coe.mpr <| by dsimp; linarith only [hpq]

